<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>API文档 - MCSG-Tencent-Cloud-API</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 2.2em;
        }

        .btn-back {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
        }

        .section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        .endpoint-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .endpoint-item {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .endpoint-item .method {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .endpoint-item .path {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .endpoint-item .description {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .code-block {
            background: #2d3748;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .code-block code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo">
                    <h1>📚 API文档</h1>
                </div>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-back">返回控制台</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>认证方式</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">所有API接口需要在请求头中添加 Authorization 字段：</p>
            <div class="code-block">
                <code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;用户名&gt;:&lt;密码&gt;</code>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>API 端点列表</h2>
            <ul class="endpoint-list">
                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/run-instance</span>
                    <span class="description">通过启动模板创建新的Minecraft服务器实例 (权限: run_instance)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/start-instance</span>
                    <span class="description">启动已停止的Minecraft服务器实例 (权限: start_instance)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/terminate-instance</span>
                    <span class="description">删除指定的Minecraft服务器实例 (权限: terminate_instance)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/instances</span>
                    <span class="description">查询当前账户下的所有Minecraft服务器实例 (权限: read_instance)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/auth-logs</span>
                    <span class="description">获取操作日志（仅管理员）(权限: admin)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/api/user-info</span>
                    <span class="description">获取当前认证用户的信息 (权限: 任意)</span>
                </li>

                <li class="endpoint-item">
                    <span class="method">GET</span>
                    <span class="path">/health</span>
                    <span class="description">健康检查（无需认证）</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>使用示例</h2>
            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin: 15px 0;">创建实例</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer admin:password" "<%= baseUrl %>/api/run-instance?templateId=lt-abc123&templateVersion=1"</code>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin: 15px 0;">获取实例列表</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer admin:password" "<%= baseUrl %>/api/instances"</code>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin: 15px 0;">获取操作日志</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer admin:password" "<%= baseUrl %>/api/auth-logs?limit=10"</code>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>MCSG-Tencent-Cloud-API | API文档</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
